'''David Young''' (1844 - 1913) was a [[Wesleyan]] minister and historian.

Young was born on 3 November 1844, near [[Haverfordwest]], later moving with his family to [[Pontlottyn]].  In 1893 Young published ''The Origin and History of Methodism in Wales'', a history of Wesleyanism in the country.  David Young died on 4 August 1913, at Margate.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://yba.llgc.org.uk/en/s-YOUN-DAV-1844.html|title=The National Library of Wales :: Dictionary of Welsh Biography|website=yba.llgc.org.uk|access-date=30 March 2017}}</ref>

