'''Mojtaba Minovi''' ({{lang-fa|مجتبی مینوی}}; February 1903 [[Tehran]] – January 1977, Tehran), the well-known [[Iran]]ian historian, literary scholar and professor of [[Tehran University]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ettelaat.com/new/index.asp?fname=2010%5C01%5C01-26%5C11-10-31.htm&storytitle=%90%D0%D4%CA%20%DA%E3%D1%20%CF%D1%20%90%E1%90%D4%CA%20%98%CA%C7%C8%CE%C7%E4%E5%9D%E5%C7=Persian-Farsi|title=Commemoration of Mojtaba Minovi in Ettelaat|publisher=(in Persian)}}</ref> he was a participant in the [[Ferdowsi Millenary|Ferdowsi Millenary celebrations]] in 1934 in [[Tehran]].
